column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY DOUBLE DECKER CHOCOLATE BAR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210406460
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sugar, glucose syrup, glucose-fructose syrup, vegetable fats (palm, shea, sunflower, rapeseed), WHEAT flour (with added calcium, iron, niacin and thiamin) cocoa butter, whole MILK powder, cocoa mass, skimmed MILK powder, whey permeate powder (from MILK), fat-reduced cocoa powder, MILK fat, emulsifiers (E442, E471, SOYA lecithin, sunflower lecithin), dried EGG white, anti-caking agent (calcium carbonate), salt, BARLEY malt extract, raising agent (E503), flavourings. MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 14% MINIMUM.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN PEANUTS, NUTS. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 04/10/2017
